org.jbei.ice.storage.model

Class SequenceFeature

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jbei.ice.storage.model.SequenceFeature
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataModel

    @Entity
public class SequenceFeature
extends Object
implements DataModel
    Stores the sequence annotation information, and associates Feature objects to a Sequence object.

    SequenceFeature represents is a many-to-many mapping. In addition, this class has fields to store sequence specific annotation information.

    Author:
    Timothy Ham, Zinovii Dmytriv
